data.description:
This beautiful home in Rancho Del Lago offers luxurious features and amenities that are sure to impress. From the moment you step through the custom security door, you'll be wowed by the stunning details and upgrades throughout.The great room is the heart of the home, featuring a beautiful stacked stone gas fireplace that creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The large windows let in plenty of natural light and provide unobstructed views of the desert and mountains that surround the community. The window treatments included offer both privacy and style, ensuring that this space is both functional and beautiful. The chef's dream kitchen is the perfect place to create culinary masterpieces, featuring executive soft-close drawers and cabinets with new hardware, custom pendant lighting over the oversized island, and luxury porcelain countertops. The stainless steel appliances, including a new sink and faucet, make meal prep a breeze. The gas cooktop with electric oven offers the best of both worlds when it comes to cooking, giving you the flexibility to create a wide range of dishes.
The primary suite of this home is a true retreat, with luxurious carpeting underfoot and stunning views of the desert. The large custom walk-in shower features a soothing rain showerhead and beautiful blue tiles that will immediately make you feel like you're at a spa. The double sink vanity offers plenty of counter space and storage, ensuring that this space is as functional as it is beautiful.
The backyard is professionally landscaped with extended pavers, electric sunshades, covered patio, hot tub (negotiable), gas stub for a grill, drip system, and gutters. The mountain and desert views will make you never want to leave. This home is located in an active adult community that offers an array of amenities, including tennis, pickleball, pool, spa, workout facilities, and a wide range of activities. It's the perfect place to live an active and social lifestyle, while also enjoying the peace and serenity of the desert.
Overall, this upgraded home in Rancho Del Lago offers luxurious features and amenities that are sure to impress. From the stunning great room and chef's dream kitchen to the luxurious primary suite and breathtaking backyard views, this home has it all. Whether you're looking for a serene place to relax or an active community to keep you busy, this home is the perfect choice.
